Subject: File System Action Module - Unicode Characters
Description: When we use the file action module to move files which contain Unicode characters the output changes these characters to "?". This means we cannot do further processing of these files as the path is no longer valid & cannot be used in the next job. During testing the issue was noticed with filenames containing Chinese characters.
Solution_Comment__c: The issue was resolved in 11.5.0.221. The customer is not ready to update SA now
